data.title: Video Games - Atari - 7800
data.meta_description: The Atari 7800 ProSystem, or simply the Atari 7800, is a home video game console officially released by Atari Corporation in 1986 as the successor to both the Atari 2600 and Atari 5200. data.text: Endless Media - I returned the LP Lilly Tomilson because I do not own a record player and I had canceled my order after I realized what I ordered was an LP record and not a CD version of that particular vocal she recorded. I returned the unopened LP to my local Walmart store so you should be receiving the unopended box soon. I am so sorry it was not what I wanted and as Lily was one of my favorite characters on "Laugh-In".
